<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>E</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Khoi ah hen na um, ngeihchun ka hnakruh, Partha bor dawh hluan, Atu ah
 lung awi tein kan hmuh cang, Pumkhat si dingah.

[C1]
   A tu ah lunglawm tein tlun inn kan in awnh hna, Hmaipanh tein rung
   lut tuah u, Thluachuah vanni za he, Rualchan cingla hawikom dawt hna, Kut
   zatial i tlai sih, Kan runinn replo tein kan in don hna, Khrihfa lungput
   ziaza tha he thih hlan i daw dingin, Cung Pathian nih lam kan hruai ko
   seh.

[V2]
 Kut zatial tlaih in ka dawt nunnem he, Zungzal leng ti sih, Hlan lio
 Adam le Eve bang lung khat in, Kan leng ti ve lai.

[C2]
   A tu ah lunglawm tein tlun inn kan in awnh hna, Hmaipanh tein rung
   lut tuah u, Thluachuah vanni za he, Rualchan cingla hawikom dawt hna, Kut
   zatial i tlai sih, Kan runinn replo tein kan in don hna, Khrihfa lungput
   ziaza tha he thih hlan i daw dingin, Cung Pathian nih lam kan hruai ko
   seh.

[V3]
 Pum hnih fonh i pumkhat chuak nang le kei, Thentu um loin, Bawipa nih
 thluachuah vanluh kan pe seh, Thla za cam ti sih.

[C3]
   A tu ah lunglawm tein tlun inn kan in awnh hna, Hmaipanh tein rung
   lut tuah u, Thluachuah vanni za he, Rualchan cingla hawikom dawt hna, Kut
   zatial i tlai sih, Kan runinn replo tein kan in don hna, Khrihfa lungput
   ziaza tha he thih hlan i daw dingin, Cung Pathian nih lam kan hruai ko
   seh.</lyrics>
<title>PAR THA BOR HLUAN CH496</title>
<hymn_number>496</hymn_number>
</song>